descript.abstract: Point features produced from the GEONAMES_ANNO_HYPSO annotation feature class representing the positioning of the annotation labels. These points may be used as substitutes for annotation in software or applications that cannot work with true annotation. To duplicate the effect of the annotation, these points should be displayed with no color or size, but they should be labeled and displayed for basemap reference.
